title: The Right Way to Do Wrong
creator: Harry Houdini
description: Librivox recording of The Right Way to Do Wrong by Harry Houdini. Read by Lee Ann Howlett. Harry Houdini, master illusionist and contortionist, unmasks the various ways that criminals take advantage of their victims. (summary by Lee Ann Howlett) For more free audiobooks, or to become a volunteer reader, please visit librivox.org. M4B format available
